---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for SolarVantage Pro — how we collect, use, and protect your information.">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: June 2026</em></p>
    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We do not collect personal information directly. Our site uses Google AdSense and affiliate links which may set cookies for analytics and personalization purposes.</p>
    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies to improve your browsing experience and serve relevant ads. You can control cookie settings through your browser preferences.</p>
    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We participate in affiliate programs (Amazon Associates, Impact, ShareASale, and others). These partners may use cookies to track referrals. We do not share any personal data with them — they only receive information that you voluntarily provide on their sites.</p>
    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may opt out of personalized advertising via your Google Ad Settings. For more information, visit the <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/">NAI opt-out page</a>.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Email: hello@solarvantagepro.com</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>